*   [Title 6](/Title_6_of_the_United_States_Code) - Domestic Security: The relatively newer addition, focusing on the protection of the homeland.
*   [Title 7](/Title_7_of_the_United_States_Code) - Agriculture: From farm to table, legally defined.
*   [Title 8](/Title_8_of_the_United_States_Code) - Aliens and Nationality: Who's in, who's out, and how they got there.
*   [Title 9](/Title_9_of_the_United_States_Code) - Arbitration: When disputes need a less dramatic resolution.
*   [Title 10](/Title_10_of_the_United_States_Code) - Armed Forces: The rules of engagement, and everything in between, for those who serve.
*   [Title 11](/Title_11_of_the_United_States_Code) - Bankruptcy: The legal framework for when financial plans spectacularly unravel.
*   [Title 12](/Title_12_of_the_United_States_Code) - Banks and Banking: The delicate art of managing money, legislatively speaking.
